---
layout: base.njk
title: "Our Tours — Heroes and Heritage Tours"
description: "Five ways to walk in their footsteps: Vimy to Victory, In Flanders Fields, The Somme Front, and our Signature and Ultimate multi-day Canadian tours."
activeNav: tours
permalink: "/tours.html"
---
{% from "partials/macros.njk" import tourCard %}

<header class="hero hero--compact">
  <div class="hero-media">
    <img src="/photos/somme/somme-06.jpg" alt="A Commonwealth War Cemetery on the Somme, framed by trees" width="1800" height="1200">
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our tours</span>
      <h1>Five ways to walk in their footsteps.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Every day tour departs from Arras and can be booked alone, or combined into a two- or three-day journey across the full Canadian story on the Western Front. All tours run in small groups of 8 guests or fewer, led personally by our guide.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">Day tours</span>
      <h2>Choose a single day, or combine all three.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="tours-grid" data-reveal>
      {% for tour in tours %}{% if not tour.combo %}{{ tourCard(tour) }}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">Multi-day tours</span>
      <h2>The complete Canadian story.</h2>
      <p class="lede">Our two most popular day tours, or all three, combined into one seamless journey — with accommodation recommendations in the old town of Arras.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tours-grid" data-reveal>
      {% for tour in tours %}{% if tour.combo %}{{ tourCard(tour) }}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="info-panel" style="position: static; margin-top: var(--space-5); max-width: 760px;" data-reveal>
      <h3>Every tour includes</h3>
      <ul class="info-panel-list">
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M3 10.5l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>An expert, English-speaking Western Front guide</li>
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M3 10.5l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>A comfortable, air-conditioned 8/9 seat mini bus</li>
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M3 10.5l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Pick-up and drop-off at Arras Train Station or your Arras accommodation</li>
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M3 10.5l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>All entry fees</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="body-text" style="font-size: 14px;">Prices are quoted in CAD. Itineraries may be varied by consensus of the guests travelling on the day. Customised and private tours are available on request — <a href="/contact.html" style="color: var(--red); font-weight: 600;">get in touch</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-reveal>
      <h2>Looking for a more personal journey?</h2>
      <p class="lede">Send us your relative's name and service details, and we'll research their story and build it into your tour.</p>
      <a href="/family-research.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Trace Your Family's Footsteps</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
